# Title: CobaltStrike Named Pipe
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Wojciech Lesicki
# Date: 2021-05-25
# Level: critical
# Description: Detects the creation of a named pipe as used by CobaltStrike
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.stealth, attack.t1055
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/pipe_created/pipe_created_hktl_cobaltstrike.yml

(PipeName="*\\MSSE-*" PipeName="*-server*") OR PipeName="\\interprocess_*" OR PipeName="\\lsarpc_*" OR PipeName="\\mojo_*" OR PipeName="\\msagent_*" OR PipeName="\\netlogon_*" OR PipeName="\\postex_*" OR PipeName="\\samr_*" OR PipeName="\\srvsvc_*" OR PipeName="\\status_*" OR PipeName="\\wkssvc_*"